1
00:00:00,016 --> 00:00:04,250
Skillberry Store. A smart skills repository for agentic
workflows.

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:11,342
Install with pip, start with make docker-run. Web UI on
port 8002, REST API on 8000. Live in under a minute.

3
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:15,637
Import any Anthropic skill via GitHub URL, zip file, or
local folder. One call — 66 tools and 43 snippets imported

4
00:00:15,687 --> 00:00:19,325
instantly.

5
00:00:20,005 --> 00:00:23,139
The Skills library auto-tags every skill with quality,
performance, and security scores generated by the AI

6
00:00:23,189 --> 00:00:26,323
plugins on import.

7
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:30,703
Execute any tool with a JSON body — via the UI dialog or
the sbs CLI. Every execution runs in a Docker sandbox,

8
00:00:30,753 --> 00:00:34,456
fully isolated.

9
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:38,221
The Content Evaluator and Security Scanner automatically
score skills on import. The Summarizer scored 9 for

10
00:00:38,271 --> 00:00:41,493
quality, 8 for performance, 8 for security.

11
00:00:42,005 --> 00:00:45,158
Three more plugins: Deduplicator finds near-identical
skills, Creator generates code from text, Optimizer runs

12
00:00:45,208 --> 00:00:48,361
Claude Code to improve skills.

13
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:52,033
Virtual MCP Servers give each skill its own MCP endpoint.
Virtual NFS mounts skills as filesystems. Prometheus and

14
00:00:52,083 --> 00:00:55,116
Jaeger built in.

15
00:00:56,026 --> 00:00:59,948
That's Skillberry Store — one service for every skill your
agents need. Find us at github.com slash skillberry-ai

16
00:00:59,998 --> 00:01:03,920
slash skillberry-store.

